You should have received the following files in the distribution tar
file for cc-mode 3.304:

    MANIFEST: This file

    cc-mode.el: Version 3.304 of the mode

    cc-mode-18.el: Emacs 18 compatibility file

    README: manual on how to use cc-mode to edit C and C++
    files. Eventually this will be replaced by a texinfo manual.

    DUMPING: A guide to ditching c-mode.el in favor of cc-mode.el.

    ChangeLog: Extremely verbose history of changes.

